<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Metanarrative&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="references-small">
<ol class="references">
